{"about_the_game":"<p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><strong>Join the cutest and most fearsome squad ever!</strong><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3363670/extras/iniciais.gif?t=1739385780\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Featuring <strong>10 unique elemental characters</strong> from \u2728 <i><strong>SHARD SQUAD</strong>\u00a0</i>\u2728, assemble your perfect team and embark on an exciting <strong>2-level adventures\u00a0</strong>full of challenges! Discover the power of team strategy and get a taste of the action that awaits you!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"> </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">In <strong>Shard Squad</strong>, help a team of elemental creatures save their lands in a thrilling and chaotic adventure filled with monsters and projectiles leaping off your screen!<img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3363670/extras/Batalha_Feito_com_o_Clipchamp-export.gif?t=1739385780\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">But don\u2019t worry\u2014great challenges come with great allies! The squad is ready to assist you, providing valuable items or even cooking up nutrients to power you up to defeat the toughest bosses.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3363670/extras/NPCS__1_.gif?t=1739385780\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">  </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Speaking of bosses, brace yourself for a wave of unique creatures constantly testing your skills. And if you manage to overcome them, an even greater calamity awaits at the end of each stage!<img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3363670/extras/Boss_Battle_Feito_com_o_Clipchamp.gif?t=1739385780\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"> </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Remember: no battle is fought alone! The squad always has each other's backs, and you get to choose who fights by your side, bringing the mechanics you need to overcome vicious hordes!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3363670/extras/Suporte_Feito_com_o_Clipchamp.gif?t=1739385780\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Face hordes! Defeat bosses! Grow stronger! And in the end, unlock new members to expand your build options and secure victory!<img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3363670/extras/Cards_Feito_com_o_Clipchamp.gif?t=1739385780\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><strong>Are you ready for the challenge?</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">  </p>","background":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3363670/page_bg_generated_v6b.jpg?t=1739385780","background_raw":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3363670/page.bg.jpg?t=1739385780","capsule_image":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3363670/49076d11414167a0222d7b130715c5c5b60e56ce/capsule_231x87.jpg?t=1739385780","capsule_imagev5":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3363670/49076d11414167a0222d7b130715c5c5b60e56ce/capsule_184x69.jpg?t=1739385780","categories":[{"description":"Single-player","id":2},{"description":"Game demo","id":10},{"description":"Steam Achievements","id":22},{"description":"Full controller support","id":28},{"description":"Steam Cloud","id":23}],"content_descriptors":{"ids":[],"notes":null},"controller_support":"full","detailed_description":"<p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><strong>Join the cutest and most fearsome squad ever!</strong><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3363670/extras/iniciais.gif?t=1739385780\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\